            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1354460534,
            "creation_date": 1354460534,
            "body": "<p>Take a look at some sorting algorithms, such as <em>bubble sort<\/em> (if it is a small set of numbers), <em>merge sort<\/em>, <em>quicksort<\/em>, and others. This is what you seem to want to do -- <em>sorting<\/em>.<\/p>\n",
